snippet.title: Hobnobbers Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the Snoozy Kazoo website for more info!
https://snoozykazoo.com/games/hobnobbers

Hobnobbers is a fast-paced 3D platformer where you and your crew of mischievous gnomish critters storm through multidimensional outlets and fight Pixys who seek to harvest you for yummy snacks. Raid the shops and stuff Shinys in your hat before the portal closes, or risk being stranded in a whimsical capitalist hellscape. Deliver your loot to Lady Goddess, an enigmatic figure trying to get revenge on her ex-husband. Trade the items you recover for cosmetic upgrades- aka drip- or, if you fail, get turned into stew!
